      • createCar

        public Car createCar(org.bukkit.Location spawnLocation,
            java.lang.String name,
            int enginePower,
            int carMass,
            double fuel,
            boolean ghost)
        Spawns a Car while creating a Car object.
        Parameters:
        spawnLocation - Location for car to appear (Note: Should be block coordinate. X+0.5, Y+1, Z+0.5)
        name - Name of Car
        mass - Mass of Car
        power - Power of Car
        fuel - Fuel of Car
        ghost - If true, the Car will not be added to the global CarMap to update it, you can then do it yourself.
        Returns:
        Car object
